    <text>
        <body>
            <p rend="indent(10)">
                <date>Sunday</date>
            </p>
            <p>My dear friend:</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">At the first opportunity, I beg of you to send me a handsome<lb/>
                prayer book in gilt, German and Polish ritual. Should you find no oppor-<lb/>tunity,
                you might send it by express. We shall see each other, God will-<lb/>ing, since I
                have received an invitation from <persName>Einstein</persName> in the form of a<lb/>
                request for information.</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">With the highest respect,</p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">Your very devoted</p>
            <p rend="indent(4)">
                <persName role="author">Jonah Bondi</persName>
            </p>
            <p><persName>Dr. Landau</persName> is very much dissatisfied with you. The views of
                    <persName>Hirsch</persName><lb/> about sects are just as false as those of
                    <persName>Felsenthal</persName> and <persName>Einhorn</persName>. I<lb/> tell
                you reformers are no sectarians but those who separated themselves<lb/> completely
                from Judaism.</p>
        </body>
    </text>
